===========================================================================
PEPPER MAKES MINT BETTER

Installing SCM Purchases Pepper
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Upload the /scmpurchases/ directory and its contents to 
   /mint/pepper/brandonkelly/. If the directory /brandonkelly/ doesn't
   exist, create it.

3. Login to your Mint installation and in the Preferences click "Install"
   under Pepper.

4. Click the SCM Purchases Pepper "Install" button. Click "Okay."

5. Make sure your System Folder Path preference is accurate.

